Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:06.05,chat,1,0000,0000,0000,,Waw! Aké pekné. Kde to sme? Na Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.57,chat,2,0000,0000,0000,,Nie celkom, stále sme v Japonsku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:10.60,chat,3,0000,0000,0000,,Ale počasie je tu podobné ako na Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.95,chat,4,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to je Haruov ostrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.32,chat,5,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je môj.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:20.34,chat,6,0000,0000,0000,,Kedysi tu bola malá dedina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:25.29,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz tu nie je nič, len dom rodiny Kujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.79,chat,7,0000,0000,0000,,Úžasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:34.58,chat,8,0000,0000,0000,,More, obloha a ostrov sú len pre mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:38.44,chat,9,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to myslí?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:42.85,chat,10,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musela prísť aj Kengova sestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.83,chat,11,0000,0000,0000,,Keďže na tomto ostrove nikto nežije,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:48.73,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,myslel som si že by to bolo dobré miesto na vymyslenie stratégie, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.02,chat,12,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, dovoľte mi teraz odísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:52.69,chat,13,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:55.18,chat,14,0000,0000,0000,,Keď budete chcieť ísť domov, zavolajte mi vysielačkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.36,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Telefóny tu nefungujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.70,chat,15,0000,0000,0000,,Správajte sa prosím slušne, uvidíme sa neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.64,title,16,0000,0000,0000,,Tieň raja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.32,chat,17,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň! Prečo to musíš robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:58.35,chat,18,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.78,chat,19,0000,0000,0000,,Stačí!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.33,chat,20,0000,0000,0000,,Zima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:09.27,chat,21,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, máš veľmi starodávny typ plaviek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.70,chat,22,0000,0000,0000,,Chlapy musia nosiť fundoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.70,note,22,0000,0000,0000,,Fundoshi: Tradičná spodná bielizeň používaná sumo zápasníkmi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.16,chat,23,0000,0000,0000,,To už nie je v móde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.29,chat,24,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Ako keby sa tebe niečo páčilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.15,chat,25,0000,0000,0000,,Presne,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.68,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to neoblečieš, Aya-chan? Vypadalo by to na tebe skvelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.47,chat,26,0000,0000,0000,,Kto  by to nosil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.63,chat,27,0000,0000,0000,,Provokuješ ma, Aya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.75,chat,28,0000,0000,0000,,Neprišli sme sa hrať-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:34.77,chat,29,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.19,chat,30,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.07,chat,31,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, to ti neodpustím!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.73,chat,32,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, ty debil! Za toto ťa zabijem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.34,chat,33,0000,0000,0000,,Kou-nii panikári.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.25,chat,34,0000,0000,0000,,Zabijem ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.63,chat,35,0000,0000,0000,,To je skvelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.01,chat,36,0000,0000,0000,,Že?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:05:00.05,chat,37,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo ty úchyl! Počkaj! Zabijem ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.68,chat,38,0000,0000,0000,,Kanpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.28,chat,39,0000,0000,0000,,Pivo pri západe slnka, to je to najlepšie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:18.45,chat,40,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Ale problém je že sú tu 2 baby pre 5-tich chalanov, takže traja si nevŕzgnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.70,chat,41,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to točíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.12,chat,42,0000,0000,0000,,Neprišli sme si sem "zavŕzgať".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:27.18,chat,43,0000,0000,0000,,Ste tu aby ste hovorili o stratégii, nie? Prečo to nerobíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.16,chat,44,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, ty vieš čo robíme?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.49,chat,45,0000,0000,0000,,Bojujete proti démonom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.44,chat,46,0000,0000,0000,,Viem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.65,chat,47,0000,0000,0000,,Mysleli ste si že som sprosté dievča, je to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.10,chat,48,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.55,chat,49,0000,0000,0000,,Takže začnime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.50,chat,50,0000,0000,0000,,Presne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.10,chat,51,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, začni.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.26,chat,52,0000,0000,0000,,Ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:59.43,chat,53,0000,0000,0000,,To ty si nás zavolal na tento ostrov. Čo ťa trápi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.85,chat,54,0000,0000,0000,,Predtým to bol Nanaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:08.39,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,teraz ženská menom Ruru ovláda Kokuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.80,chat,55,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ona len plní rozkazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.53,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,nie je to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.20,chat,56,0000,0000,0000,,Vypadá to tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.70,chat,57,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je tá osoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.32,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som si istý ale mám tušenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.92,chat,58,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš svojho dedka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.96,chat,59,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som sprostý vieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:41.82,chat,60,0000,0000,0000,,Minulých nehodách, tieň tvojho dedka sa z času na čas objavil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.38,chat,61,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, tiež si si to uvedomil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.56,chat,62,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné že hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.91,chat,63,0000,0000,0000,,Kou-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.35,chat,64,0000,0000,0000,,Nebuď opitý.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:59.36,chat,65,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie je tvoj dedko mŕtvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:06.69,chat,66,0000,0000,0000,,Môj dedko zvolal démonov aby získal nesmrteľnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.74,chat,67,0000,0000,0000,,Je možné že z temnotou uzavrel dohodu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:17.33,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,aby žil navždy a ako výmenu sa stal jednym z nich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.59,chat,68,0000,0000,0000,,Je to možné?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:25.69,chat,69,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun! Dajme si spolu kúpeľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.40,chat,70,0000,0000,0000,,Kúpeľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.02,chat,71,0000,0000,0000,,Ako minule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.26,chat,72,0000,0000,0000,,Ako minule?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.70,chat,73,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo v škôlke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.96,chat,74,0000,0000,0000,,Vy ste tam vliezli spolu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.05,chat,75,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som ti že to bolo v škôlke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:43.09,chat,76,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Kengova sestra. Sme uprostred dôležitej schôdzky-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:43.63,chat,77,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.98,chat,78,0000,0000,0000,,Aya-chan, poď sa so mnou kúpať...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.81,chat,79,0000,0000,0000,,Ty úchyl!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.64,chat,80,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa že sa atmosféra stretnutia rozbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:04.78,chat,81,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes už som sa zabavil dosť, som fakt unavený. Stretnime sa zajtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:19.34,chat,82,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.69,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Minulá noc bola dosť veterná.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.77,chat,83,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.69,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Búrka prebehla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.65,chat,84,0000,0000,0000,,Už nikdy nebudem piť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.61,chat,85,0000,0000,0000,,Pila si veľa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.61,chat,86,0000,0000,0000,,Nevypadáš dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.87,chat,87,0000,0000,0000,,Nedala som si žiaden make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.75,chat,88,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes je pekné počasie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.75,chat,89,0000,0000,0000,,Mimochodom, nevie niekto kde je môj hlučný brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.28,chat,90,0000,0000,0000,,Asi ešte spí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.18,chat,91,0000,0000,0000,,Nebol v izbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.10,chat,92,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.02,chat,93,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.55,chat,94,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, kde si?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.48,chat,95,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.42,chat,96,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.65,chat,97,0000,0000,0000,,Desné.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.24,chat,98,0000,0000,0000,,To musela byť búrka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:21.25,chat,99,0000,0000,0000,,Rádio je pokazené takže nemôžme zavolať aby nás odviezli.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:26.12,chat,100,0000,0000,0000,,Našiel som Kenga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.63,chat,101,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.88,chat,102,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.37,chat,103,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.35,chat,104,0000,0000,0000,,Je mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:57.50,chat,105,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, prečo si ma opustil? Kengo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.57,chat,106,0000,0000,0000,,To bolí...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:06.25,chat,107,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, myslím že by sme ho mali zobrať k doktorovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.79,chat,108,0000,0000,0000,,Ale rádio je pokazené, takže nemôžme zavolať doktora,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.71,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,a zobrať ho do nemocnice je vylúčené.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.54,chat,109,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme ani zavolať políciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.49,chat,110,0000,0000,0000,,Políciu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.29,chat,111,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite sa na tie zranenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.80,chat,112,0000,0000,0000,,Zranenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:28.83,chat,113,0000,0000,0000,,Kenga niekto zmlátil a potom ho hodil do mora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:30.98,chat,114,0000,0000,0000,,Bol zavraždený!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.09,chat,115,0000,0000,0000,,Ale on žije.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.28,chat,116,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš veriť že ho zabili.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:42.53,chat,117,0000,0000,0000,,Ale keď sa na to tak dívam, boli tu vražedné úmysli.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.32,chat,118,0000,0000,0000,,Ale čie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.25,chat,119,0000,0000,0000,,Na ostrove sme len my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.47,chat,120,0000,0000,0000,,Zločinec je medzi nami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.19,chat,121,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, nehovor mi že...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:03.95,chat,122,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, prečo ma obviňuješ ako prvú?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.97,chat,123,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože ty si veľmi násilná.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:12.49,chat,124,0000,0000,0000,,Bál som sa že ma tak zabiješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.07,chat,125,0000,0000,0000,,Keď si to spomenul,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.54,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Včera keď Kengo vyšiel z vody bez fundoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.28,chat,126,0000,0000,0000,,Povedala: "Zabijem ťa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.16,chat,127,0000,0000,0000,,Á-Áno, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:29.11,chat,128,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Akira povedal tú istú vec keď zletel z banánu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:34.35,chat,129,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, to mu hovorím už odmalička.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.96,chat,130,0000,0000,0000,,Aj Kou-nii tiež naňho pri potápaní zjapal že ho zabije.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:46.87,chat,131,0000,0000,0000,,Hej hej, Aki! Neobviňuj ma, Haru sa tiež nasral keď naňho Kengo špliechal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.93,chat,132,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne hej, dokonca som sa ho odvážil zabiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:57.00,chat,133,0000,0000,0000,,Hrozné! Všetci chceli zabiť Kenga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.65,chat,134,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo keď si v nebi, počuješ ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.96,chat,135,0000,0000,0000,,Je na druhom poschodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.91,chat,136,0000,0000,0000,,Sestrička chytí vrahov!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.44,chat,137,0000,0000,0000,,A pomstí tvoju smrť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.26,chat,138,0000,0000,0000,,A čo toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:27.72,chat,139,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo nemohol zaspať a tak sa praštil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.73,chat,140,0000,0000,0000,,Trieskal sa do bezvedomia a padol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.92,chat,141,0000,0000,0000,,To je možné. Hovoríme o Kengovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.37,chat,142,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.40,chat,143,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne, Kengo je magor ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.35,chat,144,0000,0000,0000,,Je tak sprostý že veľa ľudí si myslí že nie som jeho sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.36,chat,145,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím že vy dvaja ste rovnakí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:50.61,chat,146,0000,0000,0000,,Ale fakt je ten, že vrah je tu na ostrove.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.87,chat,147,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože aj na mňa zaútočil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.83,chat,148,0000,0000,0000,,Stalo sa to minulú noc,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:03.94,chat,149,0000,0000,0000,,chcela som sa ísť napiť a tak som išla do kuchyne a videla som niekoho z nej vychádzať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:09.43,chat,150,0000,0000,0000,,Čudovala som sa že prečo by niekto o takomto čase išiel von, prenasledovala som ho... ale stratila som ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.50,chat,151,0000,0000,0000,,Ledva som zdrhla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.36,chat,152,0000,0000,0000,,Nevidela si kto to bol?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.03,chat,153,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, bola tma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.53,chat,154,0000,0000,0000,,Možno to nebol chlap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:34.83,chat,155,0000,0000,0000,,Neobviňujem ťa Aya-chan, ale minulú noc si nebola v izbe, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:42.74,chat,156,0000,0000,0000,,Vošiel som potichu, ale tvoja postel bola prázdna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.93,chat,157,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si mi vliezol do izby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:53.80,chat,158,0000,0000,0000,,Um... rozmýšľal som že by sme sa mohli spoločne pozerať na hviezdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.77,chat,159,0000,0000,0000,,Ukážem ti hviezdy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.36,chat,160,0000,0000,0000,,Hviezdičky svietia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.90,chat,161,0000,0000,0000,,Minulú noc som išla vzbudiť Akiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.31,chat,162,0000,0000,0000,,Počula som čudné zvuky, a tak som si myslela že to može byť duch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:16.33,chat,163,0000,0000,0000,,Veď keď sme išli na tento ostrov Haruka-kun nám to povedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.38,chat,164,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nie je dobré sa motať okolo dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.82,chat,165,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci v dedine zomreli na mor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.21,chat,166,0000,0000,0000,,A vraví sa že... môžete vidieť ich duchov.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:36.14,chat,167,0000,0000,0000,,P-Preto som išla zobudiť Akiru aby sa mrkol či sú tu nejaký duchovia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.47,chat,168,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Akira nebol vo svojej izbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:46.81,chat,169,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Shirogane bez jediného slova odišiel a ja som ho prenasledoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.28,chat,170,0000,0000,0000,,Ale v lese som ho stratil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:56.91,chat,171,0000,0000,0000,,A nebolo to len minulú noc, chodíš von každú noc, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:01.77,chat,172,0000,0000,0000,,A niekedy keď sa nadránom vrátiš liečiš sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.80,chat,173,0000,0000,0000,,Keď to robíš sám, znamená to že majster o tom nič nevie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.83,chat,174,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-kun, až moc sa o mňa staráš a snívaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:13.17,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Snívam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.12,chat,175,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, je to len sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:21.06,chat,176,0000,0000,0000,,Nehraj sa na debila, ak je to tak, vyzleč sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.67,chat,177,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si vlastne vôbec neplával.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.96,chat,178,0000,0000,0000,,Nechceš sa vyzliecť kôli zraneniam, je to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.20,chat,179,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:29.74,chat,180,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzleč sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:34.31,chat,181,0000,0000,0000,,Nechci odo mňa aby som to urobil pred všetkými...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.66,chat,182,0000,0000,0000,,Nefrfli a vyzleč sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.06,chat,183,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.32,chat,184,0000,0000,0000,,Doriti, kam išiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.51,chat,185,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz Akira-kun, myslíš si že ten kto zabil Kenga bol Shirogane-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:54.00,chat,186,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem, viem len to že je podozrivý.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.30,chat,187,0000,0000,0000,,Môžme sa pozrieť do dediny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.18,chat,188,0000,0000,0000,,Dedina v ktorej sú duchovia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:05.63,chat,189,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to náhodou taký druh miesta kde sa ľahko rozširuje temnota?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.04,chat,190,0000,0000,0000,,OK, poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.57,chat,191,0000,0000,0000,,Í-Ísť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.36,chat,192,0000,0000,0000,,Mám z toho zlý pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.45,chat,193,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.51,chat,194,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj, vitajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.39,chat,195,0000,0000,0000,,DUCH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.37,chat,196,0000,0000,0000,,Ruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.53,chat,197,0000,0000,0000,,Dali ste si na čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:44.57,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola som si istá že prídete, Ruru vás tu od včerajška čaká.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.68,chat,198,0000,0000,0000,,Čakala si na nás?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.51,chat,199,0000,0000,0000,,No jasné, po nachystaní pasce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.99,chat,200,0000,0000,0000,,Kokuchi! Zjedzte ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.80,chat,201,0000,0000,0000,,Doppler, uvoľniť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:35.00,chat,202,0000,0000,0000,,Ruru, ako si vedela že sem prídeme?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.31,chat,203,0000,0000,0000,,Noo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.41,chat,204,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shirogane-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.47,chat,205,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:50.17,chat,206,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, ale, Shirogane-san, ako toto vysvetlíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.30,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor mi že ty a Ruru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.05,chat,207,0000,0000,0000,,Zmizni z cesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:07.99,chat,208,0000,0000,0000,,Kou a Akira-kun, porozprávajme sa hneď ako ich porazíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.27,chat,209,0000,0000,0000,,Doriti...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.90,chat,210,0000,0000,0000,,To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.62,chat,211,0000,0000,0000,,Kya- Vypadáš tak kúúl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:25.04,chat,212,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane-sama! Ideš! Ideš!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:36.42,chat,213,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane, bojujem vedľa teba a rozmýšľam či ti mám aspoň trochu veriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:41.64,chat,214,0000,0000,0000,,Trochu? Bol by som rád keby si mi veril úplne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.51,chat,215,0000,0000,0000,,Keby som mohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:50.23,chat,216,0000,0000,0000,,Ruru, poď sem a bojuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:58.52,chat,217,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, ja len plním rozkazy a bolo mi povedané aby som nebojovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.41,chat,218,0000,0000,0000,,Kto to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.49,chat,219,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.32,chat,220,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce sa stretneme len my dvaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.03,chat,221,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:08.66,chat,222,0000,0000,0000,,Čaute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.21,chat,223,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.29,chat,224,0000,0000,0000,,Utiekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.55,chat,225,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.57,chat,226,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si naozaj na našej strane, zapečať temnotu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.81,chat,227,0000,0000,0000,,Temnota sa musí premeniť na svetlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.69,chat,228,0000,0000,0000,,Temnota musí vyplniť svetlo. Vráťsa odkiaľ si prišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.18,chat,229,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.34,chat,230,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.83,chat,231,0000,0000,0000,,Uzatvoriť!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:20:01.51,chat,232,0000,0000,0000,,Čas ktorý trávim v tomto svete sa blíži ku koncu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:08.34,chat,233,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem tu byť už len chvíľku. V noci som išiel do sveta Tieňov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.48,chat,234,0000,0000,0000,,Ale oni ťa vyhnali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:18.87,chat,235,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, preto sa skrývam na kraji toho sveta, aby si telo odpočinulo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.82,chat,236,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho, veľakrát ma našli a bol som v nebezpečí
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:26.62,chat,,0000,0000,0000,,pretože Kokuchi sú v tom svete silní.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.04,chat,237,0000,0000,0000,,Ak je to tak, nemusel si to tajiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:35.31,chat,238,0000,0000,0000,,Ale to je môj problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.77,chat,239,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor s nami ako keby sme boli cudzinci.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:42.09,chat,240,0000,0000,0000,,Máš pravdu, mal som to povedať aspoň Akirovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:53.31,chat,241,0000,0000,0000,,Počkať, tak kto bol ten vrah čo zabil Kenga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.26,chat,242,0000,0000,0000,,Nebol to Shirogane?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.45,chat,243,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja som stále tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:01.11,chat,244,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, vydrž, si mŕtvy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:04.65,chat,245,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo, čo sa stalo minulú noc?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:11.29,chat,246,0000,0000,0000,,Noo... z okna som videl Akiru ako ide von,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:16.80,chat,247,0000,0000,0000,,ale stratil som sa a dostal som sa k miestu kde bola moja sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:20.17,chat,248,0000,0000,0000,,Dal som si svoje ruky na jej ramená a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.23,chat,249,0000,0000,0000,,NIE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.45,chat,250,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, to som ja, ja!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:30.29,chat,251,0000,0000,0000,,NIE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:39.24,chat,252,0000,0000,0000,,Si hrozná, Nee-chan! Môj život bol v nebezpečí!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:41.55,chat,253,0000,0000,0000,,Sú fakt sprostý, sprostý súrodenci.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.21,chat,254,0000,0000,0000,,Takže to znamená...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:46.53,chat,255,0000,0000,0000,,Zodpovedný za Kengovu smrť bola...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.41,chat,256,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo nehovorí nič okrem vtipov. Je tak sprostý.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.64,chat,257,0000,0000,0000,,OK, poďme späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:04.49,chat,258,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ako? Rádio nefunguje.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:10.07,chat,259,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme navýber, budeme tu žiť navždy, čo si myslíš, Aya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:10.76,chat,260,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslím na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:13.79,chat,261,0000,0000,0000,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:14.89,chat,262,0000,0000,0000,,To stačí!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:50.46,chat,263,0000,0000,0000,,Chlapy, dajte do toho všetko a staňte sa skvelím sluhom ako som ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.45,chat,264,0000,0000,0000,,Ovcami? To sú tie ktoré hovoria "bééé"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.45,note,264,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:53.72,chat,265,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nehovoria...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.88,chat,266,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce: Oddaný tieň
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:58.53,chat,267,0000,0000,0000,,Meee. Ale to bola koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:24:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
